  Siong7-te3 u7-chit8-kang hoa3-chong cho3 chit8-ui7 hak8-chia2, lai5-kau3 chit8-keng hak8-hau7 ian2-kang2.
  I kong2: “Tai5-gi2 chin ho2-thiaN, m7-koh chin phaiN2-oh8, m7-chai lan2 chia-e5 peng5-iu2 u7-lang5 thiaN-bo5--bo5?” I ke3-siok8 loh8-khi3 kong2, m7-kuh i khoaN3 hoan2-eng3 bo5-thang ho2, tioh8 an2-ni mng7 tak8-e5: “na2-chhiuN7 u7 ‘che’ lang5 thiaN-bo5 e5 khoan2--ou7?”
  Sui5-si5 u7 chit8-e5-lang5 peh--khi2-lai5, khi3-phut-phut kong2: “Li2 na2 e7 kong2 goa2 thiaN-bo5?” 
  “Goa2 kam2 u7 an2-ni kong2?” 
  “Li2 m7-si7 kong2 u7 chit8-e5-lang5 thiaN-bo5? Li2 kam2 m7-chai-iaN2 “oa2 si7 kok-i3-lang5”?” 
  “Goa2 chai-iaN2 li2 si7 kok-i3-lang5, m7-kuh goa2 bo5 kong2 li2 “chit-e5-lang5 “, goa2 si7 kong2 u7 “che” lang5 thiaN bo5 tai5-gi2 e5 khoan2--lah! M7-thang gou7-hoe7. M7-si7 u7 chit8-e5-lang5--lah! 
  U7 che lang5? U7 chit8-e5-lang5? U7 che lang5? U7 chit8-e5-lang5? Iah m7-si7 long2 kang7-khoan2? 
  Siong7-te3 kong2: Ah goa2 m7-si7 ka7 lin2 kong2-koe3, Tai5-gi2 chin ho2-thiaN, m7-koh chin phaiN2-oh8.
